Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.08,0:36:09.85,梢,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.85,0:36:10.69,帆,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.69,0:36:11.32,帆,,0,0,0,,今天的
